{"tid":1180099,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「下輩子再廝守」 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-05-31T14:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:40:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"034326e410300d9f6d7d3602747c88f7f1b685f3","tid":1180099,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190531/20691503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190531%2F20691503&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbZSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=6d7924f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190531%2F20691503&h=c2c735c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190531/20691503</a><br />\n<br />\n「下輩子再廝守」 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190531/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190531%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=cb82ad03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n三色台一對藝員夫婦補辦婚禮，在婚禮上煽情許諾，兩個人「下輩子再廝守」。單看字面來解讀，倒像是這輩子已經各有婚配了，所以只好寄望「下輩子」。不過他們既然這輩子已經廝守在一起，那麼，應該是下輩子還要在一起的意思。<br />\n<br />\n稍有一點點人生閱歷的人，都不應該隨便許諾，越尊重誓言的人，越慎重。以香港人平均壽命計，還有五十年壽命，未來五十年，自己變成甚麼人，對方變成甚麼人，根本無從預計，人算不如天算，世上有太多人力無法控制的因素。比如三條七跟小白襪，他們最初相遇相識的時候，又何嘗不是一臉純真的嚮往？婚禮上他們也曾許下過「愛你一輩子」的承諾吧？他們可曾想像過，到了2019年的今天，彼此會變成甚麼模樣？小白襪仍愛三條七嗎？是甚麼促使他們仍然廝守在一起？是愛還是責任？抑或是麻木？<br />\n<br />\n十三歲的人，許諾「下輩子再廝守」，尚算情真意切；三十歲的人這麼說，是肉麻當有趣，是缺乏常識，是輕率。下輩子？人類真的有下輩子嗎？就算有，這句話不該出自新婚夫婦的口，而該由已經牽手走過一輩子卻仍然相看兩不厭的老夫婦來說。<br />\n<br />\n還有，這種話更不應該公佈於眾。若干年後，說的人早已經忘記，傳媒不會忘記，翻一翻舊報道，重溫「下輩子再廝守」的許諾，當事人可能會知道自己幼稚。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n六四三十年後 (林道群)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n香港監，台灣獄 (陳也)"},{"pid":"ea0d8b1300604ea02099522a549fd78ce2a70963","tid":1180099,"uid":207208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbZSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=77c984ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}